title: Audit Log
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

After every Apply, the titles of imported tiddlers accumulate in `$:/temp/json-convert/audit-log` (a list field).  The Console renders that list as clickable links under ''Imported this session'' -- a quick way to jump straight to what you just imported.

The list resets on wiki reload because `$:/temp/...` isn't persisted.  A ''Clear log'' button forgets the list without affecting any of the actual imported tiddlers in the wiki.

The audit log only tracks //this session's// imports; it isn't a permanent history.  For that, use git or your wiki's normal save history.
